    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Quia ad animarum pertinet lucrum quicquid
                        eclesiis Dei et venerabilibus locis confertur, et hic mos ab antiquis
                        regibus inolevit ut eclesiae Dei de eorum donis et munere ditarentur.
                        Noverit omnium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque fidelium presentium
                        scilicet ac futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Chancellor #fidelisOf" ref="#people/58"
                            >Petrum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarium nostrum</rs>
                        <rs key="#fidelisOf">nobisque fidissimum</rs><rs key="#Intercessory">
                            nostram exorasse clementiam</rs>, quatenus <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/90"><rs key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs> Sancti
                            Zenonis </orgName><rs key="#Relics">ubi corpus ipsius quiescit</rs>,
                        preceptali inscriptione res pertinentes <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/510"><rs
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >de corte nostra </rs>Meleto</geogName> sitas <geogName key="#Fines"
                            ref="#estates/508"><rs key="#Fines">in Garda </rs></geogName>iuxta
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/502"><rs
                                key="#Churches">eclesiam </rs>Sancti Severi </orgName>cum <rs
                            key="#Oil">olivis</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineis </rs>ad habendum <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure perpetuo</rs> largiremur. Nos
                        igitur ratam eius arbitrantes petitionem predictas res, quae sunt <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >iugera octo</rs>, sitas in finibus Gardensis cum <rs key="#Oil"
                            >olivetis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis </rs><rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terrisque,</rs> arvis, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Hay/fodder">cultis et incultis</rs>, divisis et
                        indivisis, cum omnibus adiacentiis et pertinentiis suis sicut de corte
                        nostra Meleto pertinuerunt in integrum, ubicumque infra Gardam invente
                        fuerint, hereditario iure prefati Sancti Zenonis coenobio per hoc
                        munificentiae nostrae preceptum concedimus et firmamus. <rs key="#Manentes"
                            >manentes </rs>preterea duos, quos <persName key="#Countess"
                            ref="#people/621">Gisla </persName><rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs><orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/90"
                                ><rs key="#Monasteries"> predicto sancto loco
                        </rs></orgName>obtulit, qui pertinuerunt <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Mention #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Manentes"
                            ref="#estates/509"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Manentes"
                                ref="#places/910"><rs
                                    key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention">de
                                    curte </rs>Albareto</placeName></geogName>, quam nos eidem Gisle
                            <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">per preceptum</rs> contulimus, eidem
                        sancto coenobio ad habendum et <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >proprietario iure</rs> tenendum firmiter corroboramus. super predictas
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">quoque res </rs>illud concedimus et
                        donamus ut, sicut a divae memoriae <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/9">Hlothario</persName><rs key="#Emperor/king">
                            imperatore</rs>
                        <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">per precepti paginam</rs> concessum est,
                        liceat abbatibus prefati coenobii, qui pro tempora fuerint, <rs
                            key="#Fluvial_transport">duas naves</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rivers">in Pado </rs>et <rs key="#Rivers">in fiumine Athesis</rs>
                        et per cetera fiumina habere ad navigandum et eundum ubicumque necesse
                        fuerit absque <rs key="#Public_exactions #Datio">ulla publica exactione et
                            datione</rs>. Si quis vero umquam huius largitionis nostrae preeeptum
                        infringere et contra hoc insurgere temptaverit, nec quod voluit perficere
                        possit, sciat se compositurum viginti libras auri obrizi, medietatem palatio
                        nostro et medietatem parti ipsius coenobii cui molestia ulla illata fuerit.
                        Ut autem ab omnibus verius credatur diligentiusque observetur, manu propria
                        subter confirmavimus et muli nostri impressione insigniri iussimus. Signum
                        (MF) domni Berengarii gloriosissimi regis. <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Restaldus">Restaldus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius </rs>iussione regia ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/123">Adelardi </persName><rs
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops">episcopi et archicancellarii
                        </rs>recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SI D). Data.v. id. novemb., anno
                        incarnationis Domini .DCCCXIII., anno vero regni domni Berengarii
                        gloriosissimi regis .VI., indictione .XI. Actum <placeName ref="#places/59"
                            >Verona</placeName>. in Dei nomine feliciter, amen. </ab>
                </div>
